               <p>- Holt. I live in Marybone. This watch was pledged with me (producing it;) I believe by the prisoner at the bar, in the name of Dodd.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence.</p>
               <p>He lent me the watch, the night before; I pawned it for want of money; I was drinking with him at the Bull, and wanted money; he lent me the watch.</p>
               <p>For the Prisoner.</p>
